          <div class="faq-answer">theStacc Blog + Local bundle (~$126/mo) addresses two primary ranking factors: website content and GBP activity. Adding BrightLocal ($39/mo) enables rank tracking and citation monitoring. That's $165/month — less than most agencies charge for a strategy deck.</div>
