        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Do local businesses really need blog content for SEO?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Yes. Businesses publishing blog content rank for 3–5× more keywords versus those with only homepage and service pages. Content compounds — articles continue generating traffic for years after publication.</div>
