        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How much should a local business spend on SEO tools per month?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">A reasonable budget targets $100–200 monthly. Content automation (theStacc at $49–148/mo) or tracking suite (BrightLocal at $39–59/mo) plus citation management (Whitespark at $25/mo) covers the essentials. Don't exceed $300/month until GBP optimization is complete.</div>
