          <div class="faq-answer">Regular SEO tools target organic website rankings. Local SEO tools address Google Maps, the local 3-pack, directory listings, citations, and GBP optimization. A business can rank #1 organically but remain completely invisible in Maps.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How long does local SEO take to show results?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">GBP optimizations improve local pack rankings within 2–4 weeks. Blog content typically ranks within 60–90 days. Citation cleanup propagates across directories in 4–8 weeks. Most businesses observe measurable improvements within 3–6 months of consistent effort.</div>
